    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1642060/extras/eec5768e1dbc0b4cdaa510093f9fe2db.poster.avif?t=1761055152\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1642060/extras/eec5768e1dbc0b4cdaa510093f9fe2db.webm?t=1761055152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1642060/extras/eec5768e1dbc0b4cdaa510093f9fe2db.mp4?t=1761055152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>25年前，你的父亲登上了山顶，再也没有回来。<br>现在，他在呼唤着你。<br>《Broken Spectre》是一款大型恐怖叙事游戏，与《布莱尔女巫计划》的制作者合作开发。<br>凯西的父亲留下了一条神秘的信息，带领她回到Cold'blood山荒弃的小径上，这个遥远的荒野世代以来一直困扰着她的家族。<br>一股可怕的力量在山上潜伏，注视着凯西的每一个动作。<br>凯西能否利用父亲留下的线索找到他？ <br>或者，其它什么东西会先找到她？<br>触摸恐怖<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1642060/extras/792a63a2d177d46bfb83fc4283e8f6d7.poster.avif?t=1761055152\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1642060/extras/792a63a2d177d46bfb83fc4283e8f6d7.webm?t=1761055152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1642060/extras/792a63a2d177d46bfb83fc4283e8f6d7.mp4?t=1761055152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《Broken Spectre》利用Quest沉浸式手部追踪控制，将游戏中可怕的身体恐怖元素带到了前所未有的逼真境地。<br>独特的大型恐怖叙事<br>由《布莱尔女巫计划》的制作人制作，《Broken Spectre》是一款受到约翰·卡朋特（John Carpenter）和H.P.洛夫克拉夫特（H.P. Lovecraft）作品启发的原创大型恐怖体验游戏。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1642060/extras/34ed9e65e6502d32d7d13fecd82b10db.poster.avif?t=1761055152\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstati